</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5930/off-center-text-in-status-bar/?comment=5931#comment-5931</link><description>I can't seem to upload images or files. The loading icon never goes away and when i press "ok" it just stops. Any suggestions on how to show images?</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2015 18:14:59 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5930/off-center-text-in-status-bar/?comment=5931#comment-5931</guid></item><item><title>Answer by TheRoach for &lt;p&gt;The text in my status bar and workspace buttons floats to the top of the bar. I would like it to be centered vertically. Is this possible?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am using i3 gaps by airblader, but i recall having the same issue with vanilla i3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is an image of the off center text i am describing:
&lt;a href="http://i.imgur.com/nxmYAzb.png"&gt;default height&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

